Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.26,0:02:20.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,野口 你在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.18,0:02:22.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肥皂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.56,0:02:25.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想着去市场上卖了当做社团基金
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.89,0:02:27.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能做肥皂哇？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.56,0:02:28.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.90,0:02:30.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看 就像这样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.53,0:02:34.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个就是我们部春天的新作
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.11,0:02:36.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾草巧克力香蕉味
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.95,0:02:38.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好臭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.37,0:02:42.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,野口 这个卖不出去的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.33,0:02:43.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是失礼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.29,0:02:44.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可是混合了艾草的杀菌成分
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.79,0:02:45.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有巧克力和香蕉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.21,0:02:49.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三种提高女性好感度的必备要素哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.46,0:02:53.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.51,0:03:00.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你打翻了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.68,0:03:03.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然是贵重的艾草油和西柚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.23,0:03:08.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.11,0:03:10.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个味道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.40,0:03:13.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很清爽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.65,0:03:16.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像有很好闻的味道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.74,0:03:19.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你 good job
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.24,0:03:21.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你 nice guy
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.78,0:03:24.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎来到放科部
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.33,0:03:31.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说早田老师你来这里干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.46,0:03:33.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 忘记正事了
