Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.35,0:03:48.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能要留级
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.10,0:03:50.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你能帮帮他吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.86,0:03:53.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害的说明
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.86,0:03:56.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.99,0:03:59.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一边工作
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.24,0:04:01.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那可真是不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.99,0:04:03.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是勤劳青年嘛？
